The CAS library is sympy.

Code works on Debian Wheezy
Code works on Mac OS X Tiger (10.4.11) with fink distribution for python (2.7.5) and latex (pdfTeX 3.1415926-2.3-1.40.12 (TeX Live 2011/Fink) )

export PYTHONPATH=<clone dir>/sympy
python ./CL1_4.py
